text: Ðis synt þara X hida land gemære to Cliftune.
Ærest afene stream healt þone norð ende.
Of afene upp on smalancumbes broc.
Þonne of holan wege suð on ecge on Hygelaces get.
Þonne on ærning hyrste on þa hege ræwe.
Andlang broces upp in horscumbes heafod.
Þonne suð rihte on Wodnes dic.
Upp eft on smalen cumbes broc.
